00:26:26,264 --> 00:26:28,193
Tak masuk akal!/
Tak masuk akal!

456
00:26:28,194 --> 00:26:30,032
Akui kenyataan dia hanya berusaha membela diri!

457
00:26:30,033 --> 00:26:31,923
Akui itu!/
Akui itu!

458
00:26:32,204 --> 00:26:34,802
Kwon Byeonhosa-nim, aku menemukan kasus
